Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.35,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(402,470)}木叶的苍蓝野兽 登场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多少次…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不仅头脑聪明 而且胆识过人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我很温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向来反对打柔弱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你怎么看…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不像柔弱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你解除了幻术 但不要太嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能完全困住她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的查克拉到底有多强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么近距离的束缚都被压回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一放手 肯定会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只能用那个忍术解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一击都没中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待已久的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人野心的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 干吗和这种家伙混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都爬到了树顶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和你较量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把佐助…带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到我说的没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复苏的木叶美丽之苍蓝野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浓…浓眉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浓眉 你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去追佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人 请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浓眉 当心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会用自己的骨头攻击对手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的能力深不可测啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还磨蹭什么 快去追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是以帅气的姿势答应过小樱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把佐助给带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一生的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人 就由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浓眉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该没工夫东张西望了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便那个棺桶里装的是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:12:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭下忍小队也很难对付他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们上忍都弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该派遣特别小队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去援助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从大蛇丸袭击这里之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶已经丧失了作为大国的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止国内外的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下所有上忍 中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都处于总动员的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便写轮眼落入大蛇丸之手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当务之急还是避免与他国的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大蛇丸的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能由着他去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他恢复了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会卷土重来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想好对策了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 凯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么累成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务出什么状况了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 完成任务之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻飞奔回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 小李的手术情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修炼忍术什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就可以开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是先让他静养一阵子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…不好了 第五代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李洛克不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 该做个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 趁我治疗弦间和雷同时跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追那些家伙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还相当慌忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把药瓶和我的酒瓶拿混了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 凯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 小李他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍微沾一点酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会…变得非常可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶大旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体很灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有踢中他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体柔韧得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作也很独特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的攻击太单调了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我差不多该吃药了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准时吃药是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就讨厌吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前为了庆祝他学会里莲华
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地带小李出去吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他把我的酒当水喝了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就喝了一小杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝下之后 发生了可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若暴风雨扫过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭店已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经一塌糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药的味道总是怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这家伙到底喝了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭店变得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人 小李他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发很大的酒疯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是一个天生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉拳好手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的策略如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是忍者的精髓所在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯老师 我又成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中的世界 飘飘荡荡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己肯定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:22:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兽爆发 跳吧 飞吧 冲吧